title: Dell Studio 1749 Win 7 HP x64 Recovery Disks
description:
Dell Studio 1749 Windows 7 Home Premium x64 Recovery Disks

These are the disks created from the Dell Datasafe Local Backup program when the computer is new. 

This software may not contain all necessary drivers for your exact model.

Disk 1 MD5: 9DF816833EEE1CCED998ABB8DDFA1FE8

Disk 2 MD5: D8C2C21E8CBCA37C34D4AC1D7F68B5AC

These disks should also work with the Dell Studio 1747 since they are similar hardware, but has not been tested.

I would recommend after all updates are applied and everything is the way you want then do a Windows 7 full system image backup.
